  "title": "Rich Savory Malaysian Chicken Curry",
  "description": "A salty and comforting Malaysian dish featuring lemongrass and low-fat friendly ingredients, this curry is perfect for a weeknight dinner. It has a glassy-jelly texture that is sure to please.",
